author: Kiley W.
description: A cog for managing and tracking user levels and XP in Discord servers.
install_msg: Thank you for installing the Leveling cog. This cog tracks user levels and XP based on message activity.
short: Manages user levels and XP in Discord servers.
end_user_data_statement: This cog stores user leveling data for the purpose of tracking and managing levels and XP within the server.
